clinical_study.brief_title: Safety and Efficacy Study of Dysport RU and Glabellar Lines
clinical_study.official_title: A Phase II, Double Blind, Randomised, Placebo and Active Comparator Controlled Study to Assess the Safety and Efficacy of Three Doses of Dysport RU (20 U, 50 U, and 75 U) Administered as a Single Treatment Cycle to Improve the Appearance of Moderate to Severe Glabellar Lines

brief_summary.textblock: The primary objective is to assess the dose response versus placebo of a single treatment of Dysport RU (Dysport RU, Ready to Use, for injection), for the improvement in appearance of moderate to severe glabellar lines at maximum frown.

primary_outcome.measure: Percentage of Subjects as Responders in the ILA (Using Validated 4-point Photographic Scale) and the SSA of Glabellar Lines at Maximum Frown

secondary_outcome.measure: Percentage of Subjects as Assessed as Responders, by Both Investigator's Live Assessment and the Subject's Self-assessment at Maximum Frown.
secondary_outcome.description: A responder at maximum frown was defined as a subject having a severity grade of none or mild at maximum frown on the visit day and a severity grade of moderate or severe at maximum frown at Visit 2.

criteria.textblock:
Inclusion Criteria:
- Female between 30 - 60 years of age
- Moderate to severe vertical glabellar lines at maximum frown at baseline
Exclusion Criteria:
- Silicone injections into the upper face
- Any prior treatment with fillers (e.g. collagen-type implants) skin abrasions or photorejuvenation within the previous 12 months
- Any planned facial cosmetic surgery during the study period
- A history of ablative skin resurfacing of the area to be treated during the study.

participant_flow.recruitment_details: Study was performed as a multicentre study at eight investigational sites in France and Germany. Date of first enrolment: 30-Mar-2011 and Date of last completed: 27-Sep-2011.
participant_flow.pre_assignment_details: A total of 178 patients were screened. 2 patient did not meet the entry criteria. 176 patients were randomized.Patients were randomized into 5 groups.

group.title: Placebo
group.description: Intramuscular injections on Day 1 (total injection volume of 0.25 ml divided into five intramuscular injections of 0.05 mL per injection each of which was injected into five pre-defined sites across the glabellar region) (single treatment cycle)

group.title: Dysport NG 20 U
group.description: Botulinum type A toxin (Dysport RU), Intramuscular injections on Day 1 in the muscle (total injection volume of 0.25 ml divided into five intramuscular injections of 0.05 mL per injection each of which was injected into five pre-defined sites across the glabellar region) (single treatment cycle) Ready to Use (RU)
